tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic (
    visitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    page_visited VARCHAR,
    conversion_status BOOLEAN,
    user_behavior JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE website_traffic ( 
  id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
  visitor_id INT, 
  page_id INT, 
  timestamp TIMESTAMP, 
  traffic_source VARCHAR(100) 
);

CREATE TABLE conversion_rates ( 
  id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
  page_id INT, 
  conversion_id INT, 
  conversion_rate DECIMAL(5, 2), 
  timestamp TIMESTAMP 
);
